  "report_text": "# Observability and Tracing\n\nPublic observability materials make traces, spans, and diagnostic visibility explicit parts of AI system operation rather than hidden implementation details.[1][2]\n\nAt the same time, the public materials leave some uncertainty about how much observability platforms own evaluation workflows versus simply exposing telemetry for other systems to interpret.[1][2]\n",
